data.description: Well below market value.  Recent appraisal came in at $1,750,000 (see attached) This brand-new home is complete and  is sure to check all the boxes.  30 minutes to Ellsworth and Bar Harbor.  Oceanfront with level access which is rare in Maine.  Breath taking views of Frenchman Bay and MDI.  Michael Maines design for a passivhaus house.  Enjoy the low cost of heat with views out the triple paned windows.  Plumbed for an endless pool or hot tub in great room that opens out directly to the ocean.
